rows.label: bf02290100_0020
rows.name:
That shrew thinks she owns the place, just
because she curries favor with the Emperor...

rows.label: bf02290100_0030
rows.name: If only I'd got the Holy Grail myself.

rows.label: bf02290100_0040
rows.name:
I could have returned home in triumph,
or sold her to Bahn for a tidy sum...

rows.label: bf02290100_0050
rows.name:
But it's not over. I refuse to
let this place be the end of me!

rows.label: bf02290100_0060
rows.name:
I will not be left to rot in
this flea-bitten backwater!

rows.label: bf02290100_0090
rows.name:
Double the number of guardsmen!
Round up whoever you can find!

rows.label: bf02290100_0100
rows.name:
We're going to find that Holy Grail
before Meleph gets her paws on her.
